Out of nowhere, a speeding car blindsides Karissa (Meryll Soriano) and hurls her delicate body into the air. She feels herself being suddenly lifted into the air, floating, suspended, spinningÃ¢â‚¬Â¦ Then pain. Chaos. Darkness. Silence. She lays face down on the pavement. Dead.

Anton (Ping Medina), who always loved her in secret, holds her lifeless body in his arms. The loss and sadness unbearable. He reaches his threshold, this tragic event being the last thread to make his decision, to take the final leap. If only to save his beloved.

